headline: TotalEnergies, Emerson announce strategic collaboration
summary: TotalEnergies (TTE) and Emerson’s (EMR) Aspen Technology business have announced a strategic collaboration to deploy advanced digital technologies for the continuous, real-time collection of data from TotalEnergies’ industrial sites.
